OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FBlackpool's Tramtown museum has been
OL,8,Fforced to close permanently after an
OL,9,Findependent survey found the main
OL,10,Fbuilding to be unsafe and facing
OL,11,Fdemolition.
OL,13,FThe closure brings down the curtain on
OL,14,Fthe popular Rigby Road visitor
OL,15,Fattraction, it's the workshop where
OL,16,Fseveral of the heritage trams are
OL,17,Fkept, along with all the machinery
OL,18,Fthat is needed for their maintenance.
OL,20,FThe building dates back to the 1920s.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
