FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FMany of Blackpool's famous heritage
OL,8,Ftrams are housed in a separate
OL,9,Fbuilding opposite the museum
OL,11,FThe Leader of Blackpool Council
OL,12,Finsists it is not the end for
OL,13,FBlackpool's heritage trams
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FCllr Lynn Williams said: "While the
OL,8,Fwork was ongoing fixing the electrics
OL,9,Fat Tramtown, an independent structural
OL,10,Fengineer carried out a survey of the
OL,11,Fbuilding. That independent report has
OL,12,Fcome back saying that the building is
OL,13,Funsafe. The only public entrance is
OL,14,Funsafe and we can't gamble with the
OL,15,Fsafety of volunteers and visitors by
OL,16,Fopening an unsafe building. Equally,
OL,17,Fbad weather last month ripped even
OL,18,Fmore panels off the roof which has led
OL,19,Fto it leaking again.
OL,26,@oD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,F"We have looked to quickly and safely
OL,8,Fremove everything out of the building
OL,9,Fand find a place to store and preserve
OL,10,Fit. Unfortunately for the building
OL,11,Fitself there is no safe or affordable
OL,12,Falternative but demolition.
OL,14,FTramtown Museum is run by dedicated
OL,15,Fvolunteers who heard the news about
OL,16,Fthe demolition from Blackpool
OL,17,FTransport at the weekend
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FClly Lynn Williams said: "We
OL,8,Fappreciate this closure will be
OL,9,Fdifficult for the Tramtown volunteers
OL,10,F, and for people who care about our
OL,11,Fheritage and our trams just as I do.
OL,12,FMyself and the new managing director
OL,13,Fof Blackpool Transport are on the same
OL,14,Fpage that we want Tramtown to open for
OL,15,Fthe summer and are looking at every
OL,16,Fpossible solution to find a pop-up
OL,17,Fsite for it to reopen as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FCllr Paul Galley, who is also leader
OL,8,Fof Blackpool's Council's Conservative
OL,9,Fopposition group and the volunteer
OL,10,Fcoordinator at Tramtown, said he had
OL,11,Fbeen told by Blackpool Transport that
OL,12,Fthe fitting shop was "uninhabitable".
OL,14,FHe said: "That raises a lot of
OL,15,Fquestions around why the volunteers of
OL,16,FTramtown, the public, the MP, the
OL,17,FCouncil Leader were allowed in, when
OL,18,Fit was uninhabitable.
OL,26,@tD@VOUtD@dO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FCllr Galley says his suggestion that
OL,8,FTramtown could become part of the
OL,9,FBlackpool Heritage and Museum Trust,
OL,10,Fwhich he said could safeguard the
OL,11,Famenity, has not been taken up.
OL,13,FCouncil leaders are now working on a
OL,14,Fjoint funding bid and steering group
OL,15,Fto secure a better future for Tramtown
OL,16,Fand its historic trams.
OL,18,FAll funds raised by Tramtown are held
OL,19,Fin a separate account, the council
OL,20,Fconfirmed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
