CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777464668
OL,3,CBlackpool's Tramtown Museum shuts
OL,4,Cpermanently as building faces
OL,5,Cdemolition
OL,7,FBlackpool Transport's new Managing
OL,8,FDirector, Lea Harrison, has said the
OL,9,Frevitalisation of heritage operations
OL,10,Fis one of his top priorities, as well
OL,11,Fas finding a permanent home for an
OL,12,Fimproved heritage tram attraction:
OL,14,F"Blackpool is as famous for its
OL,15,Fhistoric trams as it is for its tower
OL,16,Fand the Pleasure Beach and we are
OL,17,Ffully committed to preserving the
OL,18,Ftown's rich tramway heritage for
OL,19,Ffuture generations to enjoy,"
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
